'''大年结实'''是某些[[多年生植物|多年生植物]]种群[[果实|果实]]产量会周期性地发生巨大差异的一种[[自然现象|自然现象]]<ref name="biods.2019312" /><ref name="Norton2389413" />。这一类[[植物|植物]]在某些年份会大量结实（大年）, 而在其他年份很少或根本不结实（小年）<ref name="biods.2019312" />。这是[[植物|植物]]适应环境、提高繁殖能力的一种策略<ref name="biods.2019312" />，同时也受到气候因素的直接影响<ref name="annurev.ecolsys.33.020602.095433" />。大年结实现象主要发生在[[风媒传粉|风媒传粉]]的树种中，但也出现在[[龙脑香科|龙脑香科]]和[[禾本科|禾本科]]植物中<ref name="Norton2389413">{{cite journal |last1=Norton |first1=D. A. |last2=Kelly |first2=D. |title=Mast Seeding Over 33 Years by Dacrydium cupressinum Lamb. (rimu) (Podocarpaceae) in New Zealand: The Importance of Economies of Scale |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_functional-ecology_1988_2_3/page/399 |journal=Functional Ecology |date=1988 |volume=2 |issue=3 |pages=399 |doi=10.2307/2389413}}</ref><ref name="annurev.ecolsys.33.020602.095433">{{cite journal |last1=Kelly |first1=Dave |last2=Sork |first2=Victoria L. |title=Mast Seeding in Perennial Plants: Why, How, Where? |journal=Annual Review of Ecology and Systematics |date=2002-11 |volume=33 |issue=1 |pages=427–447 |doi=10.1146/annurev.ecolsys.33.020602.095433}}</ref>。在依赖[[动物|动物]]扩散[[种子|种子]]的植物中, 大年结实被认为是植物通过控制动物的贮食行为提高[[种子扩散|种子扩散]]效率, 增加繁殖成功率的一种策略。<ref name="biods.2019312">{{cite journal |last1=Yang |first1=Xifu |last2=Zhang |first2=Hongmao |last3=Zhang |first3=Zhibin |title=Mast seeding and its relationship to animal hoarding behaviour |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-07-20 |volume=28 |issue=7 |pages=821 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019312}}</ref>

